  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Tuladha kode, JSON Schema, saha cithakan kabijakan ingkang saged dipunwaos mesin dipunlisensi mawi Lisensi MIT, kajawi dipunsebataken sanès. Panjenengan kepareng masang menika ing situs panjenengan piyambak kanthi bébas.",
