  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "Kadhawuhaken sasampunipun KTT Keamanan AI Bletchley saha dipunpimpin déning Yoshua Bengio mawi langkung saking 100 ahli saking meh 30 negara, ugi PBB, OECD, saha Uni Eropa, laporan mandhiri menika ngringkes bukti ilmiah samenika babagan kapasitas saha risiko AI unggulan — kanthi nyatet bilih sawetara sistem samenika saged ngenali menawi lagi dipunevaluasi saha ngowahi tumindakipun miturut menika.",
