  "Correct positioning: independent research drafts, protocol proposals, and an open specification experiment.": "Posisi ingkang leres: rancangan riset mandhiri, usulan protokol, saha eksperimen spesifikasi ingkang mbuka.",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Belgium (BE) now maps to Dutch instead of French — Flemish speakers are the country’s majority (~60%) over Walloon French speakers (~40%).": "Ndandosi setelan standar sadèrèngipun: Belgia (BE) samenika dipunpetakaken dhateng basa Walanda tinimbang basa Prancis — penutur Flandria minangka mayoritas negara menika (~60%) ngungkuli penutur Prancis Walonia (~40%).",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Kazakhstan (KZ) now maps to Kazakh instead of Russian, now that a Kazakh translation exists — the same kind of fix as the earlier Belgium correction.": "Ndandosi setelan standar sadèrèngipun: Kazakhstan (KZ) samenika dipunpetakaken dhateng basa Kazakh tinimbang basa Rusia, sarehne samenika sampun wonten terjemahan Kazakh — jenis pandandosan ingkang sami kaliyan pandandosan Belgia sadèrèngipun.",
  "Could AI Be Conscious?": "Could AI Be Conscious?",
