  "Custom tier": "Tataran kustom",
  "Daily Nous reports on a retracted Journal of Medical Ethics submission containing multiple fabricated, AI-hallucinated references — complete with fake university affiliations and defunct email addresses — that the author reportedly left uncorrected even after being given a chance to fix proofs. The piece contrasts this with Bioethics, whose automated reference-checking would have caught the problem, and argues the real bottleneck isn't detection technology (one commenter's script flagged the fake citations in under a minute) but unpaid reviewer labor and publishing incentives that reward throughput over scrutiny.": "Daily Nous nglaporaken babagan naskah Journal of Medical Ethics ingkang dipuntarik malih amargi ngemot kathah referensi palsu asil halusinasi AI — komplit mawi afiliasi universitas palsu saha alamat email ingkang sampun boten aktif — ingkang miturut kabar penulisipun mboten dipundandosi sanajan sampun dipunparingi kesempatan kanggé ndandosi proof. Tulisan menika mbandhingaken kaliyan Bioethics, ingkang pemeriksaan referensi otomatisipun mesthinipun saged nyekel masalah menika, saha ngandharaken bilih hambatan sabenaripun sanès teknologi deteksi (skrip setunggal komentator saged nandhingi kutipan palsu menika kirang saking setunggal menit), nanging tenaga reviewer ingkang mboten dipunbayar saha insentif penerbitan ingkang ngajèni volume tinimbang ketelitian.",
  "Data free-riding vs. trillion-dollar AI valuations": "Panganggé data tanpa mbayar (free-riding) tandhing kaliyan penilaian AI ing skala triliunan dolar",
  "DeepMind CEO calls for an independent standards body to regulate frontier AI": "DeepMind CEO calls for an independent standards body to regulate frontier AI",
  "Demis Hassabis proposed a FINRA-style regulator for frontier model releases: labs would submit models for review up to 30 days before deployment, voluntary at first, with a path toward mandatory compliance in the US market.": "Demis Hassabis ngusulaken regulator model FINRA kanggé rilis model unggulan: laboratorium badhé nyerahaken model kanggé dipuntinjau ngantos 30 dinten sadèrèngipun dipunpasang, sacara sukarela ing mangsa awal, mawi jalan tumuju kepatuhan wajib ing pasar Amerika Serikat.",
  "Denied": "Dipuntolak",
  "Deployable policy starter template": "Cithakan awalan kabijakan ingkang saged dipunpasang",
  "Deployable policy starter template at /downloads/agiright-policy-starter.zip — a minimal static site with the full machine-readable layer, ready for Cloudflare Pages or any static host.": "Cithakan awalan kabijakan ingkang saged dipunpasang, ing /downloads/agiright-policy-starter.zip — situs statis minimal mawi lapisan lengkap ingkang saged dipunwaos mesin, siap kanggé Cloudflare Pages utawi host statis menapa kémawon.",
  "Deploying machine-readable policies on your site": "Masang kabijakan ingkang saged dipunwaos mesin ing situs panjenengan",
  "Disclaimer": "Sangkalan",
  "Distinct from human UI, SEO, or plain APIs, the AI Ingestion & Capability Layer gives websites a machine-facing architecture: a Manifest Layer (entry points like /llms.txt and /ai/manifest.json), a Corpus Layer (machine-readable knowledge), a Capability Layer (agent-callable tools), and a Governance Layer (provenance, licensing, versioning). Static-first, upgradeable toward APIs and MCP. Note: in this paper AICL names the ingestion architecture; on this site's protocol pages AICL refers to the AI Content Licensing Layer.": "Bénten kaliyan UI kanggé manungsa, SEO, utawi API biasa, AI Ingestion & Capability Layer maringi situs web arsitektur ingkang ngadhep dhateng mesin: Lapisan Manifest (gerbang mlebet kadosta /llms.txt saha /ai/manifest.json), Lapisan Korpus (kawruh ingkang saged dipunwaos mesin), Lapisan Kapasitas (piranti ingkang saged dipunpanggil agen), saha Lapisan Tata Kelola (asal-usul, lisensi, versi). Utamanipun statis, saged dipuntingkataken dhateng API saha MCP. Cathetan: ing makalah menika AICL nyebataken arsitektur ingestion; ing kaca-kaca protokol situs menika, AICL nudhuhaken dhateng Lapisan Lisensi Konten AI.",
  "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm": "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm",
  "Docs": "Dokumen",
  "Docs / Examples": "Dokumen / Tuladha",
  "Document library": "Pustaka dokumen",
  "Does AI have rights — and which framings are even coherent?": "Menapa AI gadhah hak — saha kerangka mikir ingkang pundi ingkang koheren?",
  "Download": "Undhuh",
  "Draft status": "Status rancangan",
  "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026": "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026",
  "Educational demo: HMAC-SHA256 with a shared secret, showing request-bound, expiring, verifiable license tokens. Production tokens should be signed asymmetrically, with the publisher’s public key discoverable under /.well-known/.": "Demo édukasi: HMAC-SHA256 mawi rahasia ingkang dipunbagi, nedahaken token lisensi ingkang kaiket kaliyan panyuwunan, gadhah wates wekdal, saha saged dipunverifikasi. Token produksi kedahipun dipuntandhatangani sacara asimetris, mawi kunci umum penerbit ingkang saged dipunpanggihaken wonten ing /.well-known/.",
  "Eight more /topics entries, this time researched by an AI agent rather than curated by hand — same rule as before: every source fetched and confirmed live, summaries an original paraphrase, before anything gets added. 14 entries total.": "Wolung entri /topics tambahan, ingkang sepisan menika dipunriset déning agen AI, sanès dipunkurasi kanthi tangan — aturanipun tetep sami kados sadèrèngipun: saben sumber dipunjupuk saha dipunkonfirmasi langsung, ringkesan minangka parafrase asli, sadèrèngipun menapa kémawon dipuntambahaken. Total 14 entri.",
  "Email": "Surel",
